    <p style="color:#a9bad3;margin-top:14px;font-size:18px;line-height:1.75">
      Every expiring LIHTC building in a neighbourhood that got nicer is this same story.
      The tenants stayed. The value arrived. And the value is about to leave without them.
    </p>
